Description: BW Offshore Limited is a Bermuda-based holding company that owns and operates oil and gas floating, production, storage and offloading vessels (FPSOs). The Companyâ€™s activities are construction, lease and operation of FPSOs as well as offshore floating wind. The Company has a fleet of approximately 10 FPSOs, operating in Africa, Europe, Southeast Asia & Oceania, and Americas. The Company owned fleet included the vessels, such as Abo FPSO, BW Adolo, Espoir Ivoirien, Petroleo Nautipa, Sendje Berge, BW Athena, BW Catcher, BW Cidade de Sao Vicente, BW Pioneer, FPSO Polvo, YUUM Kâ€™AKâ€™NAAB, BW Joko Tole, BW Opportunity and Umuroa.
